                    <li>‚úì <b>Shredding items ready</b> - Go to: <i>Shredding &gt; Inventory Items</i></li>
                    <li>‚úì <b>Work orders created</b> - Group items into jobs</li>
                </ul>
                <p><b>üìã To create a shredding batch:</b></p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click <b>New</b> to create a batch</li>
                    <li>Enter a <b>Batch Name</b> (e.g., "Weekly Shredding - Jan 15, 2024")</li>
                    <li>Group multiple shredding inventory items</li>
                    <li>Click <b>Save</b> to create the batch</li>
                </ol>
                <p><b>üöÄ Key Features:</b><br/>
                ‚Ä¢ <b>Batch processing:</b> Group multiple items for efficiency<br/>
