                <p><b>üí° Pro Tips:</b><br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Batch items by customer for consolidated billing<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Use consistent naming: "YYYY-MM-DD CustomerName" or "WeekN-YYYY"<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Group by route for efficient pickup scheduling<br/>
                </p>
            </field>
        </record>
    </data>
</odoo>
